  "elapsed_s": 160.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--1944 [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in the liberated city of Kaunas, Kovno, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in contact with Captain Gusev from the border patrol [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in the Russian Army.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Basically, the unit which Captain Gusev approached me with was the-- they were called in Russian, [SPEAKING RUSSIAN], NKVD.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That is a border patrol unit which is-- during the peacetime, they are the border patrol.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "During wartime, they're a department of the NKVD and very respected unit and very effective.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this is a unit-- regiments-- it's composed from regiments which-- each of the regiment had a number.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Our number was the [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Regiment Number 33.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We-- the uniform that we used to wear was green and green hats.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And our mission, basically, was to follow the front line and screen right up to the front line.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "After the-- they take over a city, our mission was to find out what kind of resistance-- and everything connected with, with, cleaning up the pockets of resistance.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Everything connected with investigative forces-- investigate whether there is some, some, some sabotage or something that is being planned against the military-- the incoming and liberating military forces.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Before-- as soon I met with Captain Gusev, he explained to me-- he gave me the-- a-- he read me my, my obligations and what actually he plans to do with our group.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And specially-- specifically, he told me that they are going to use me in the beginning, after giving me a certain short-time training in the military because I have never been to the military.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So they have to give me a, a short, extensive training.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And right after that, I'm going to be absorbed within the-- within the-- within this unit, within this regiment.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
